              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Full pipeline — research, brief, write, optimise, publish</li>
                <li>Auto-publishes to WordPress / Webflow / Ghost</li>
                <li>30 SEO articles a month, scheduled</li>
                <li>Bundle adds Local SEO + Social at $167/mo</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Not a keyword research dashboard</li>
                <li>Built for content, not technical audits</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
