            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Backlink data not as deep as Ahrefs</li>
                <li>UI takes a week to learn</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Operators wanting one tool for everything except content.</div>
